<h1>Privacy Policy — Vector</h1>
<p class="updated">Last updated: 21 July 2026</p>

<p>Vector is an astrology and numerology app. This policy explains what the app
does with your information. The short version: your birth details stay on your
device, and we do not run analytics, advertising, or tracking of any kind.</p>

<h2>What the app stores</h2>
<p>To calculate your chart and matrix, the app asks for and stores on your device:</p>
<ul>
  <li>your name (optional) and gender (optional);</li>
  <li>your date of birth, and time of birth if you know it;</li>
  <li>your place of birth — its name, coordinates and time zone;</li>
  <li>the life areas you chose to focus on and your mood check-ins;</li>
  <li>app settings: language, notification preferences, reading streak, and any
      answer packs you have purchased.</li>
</ul>
<p>All of this is kept in the app's local database on your device and in a shared
container used by the Vector home-screen widget. None of it is sent to us, and we
have no server that holds a copy. Deleting the app removes it.</p>

<h2>What leaves your device</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Place lookup.</strong> When you type your birth place, the text you
      enter is sent to Apple's geocoding service to turn it into coordinates and a
      time zone. This is handled by Apple under
      <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/">Apple's privacy policy</a>.
      We never receive the query.</li>
  <li><strong>Purchases.</strong> Subscriptions and answer packs are processed by
      Apple through the App Store. The app never sees or stores your payment
      details — it only learns whether a purchase is active.</li>
  <li><strong>Text generation.</strong> Vector currently composes all readings on
      your device. If online generation is enabled in a future version, only
      already-computed values — zodiac sign numbers, numerology digits, and the
      current date — would be sent. Your name, exact birth time, coordinates and
      place name would not be included.</li>
</ul>

<h2>What we do not do</h2>
<ul>
  <li>No analytics, crash-reporting, or advertising SDKs are present in the app.</li>
  <li>We do not create accounts and do not ask for your email or phone number.</li>
  <li>We do not sell, rent, or share personal data with third parties.</li>
  <li>We do not track you across other apps or websites.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Notifications</h2>
<p>If you allow notifications, reminders are scheduled locally by your device.
No push server is involved and no data leaves your phone to deliver them.</p>

<h2>Children</h2>
<p>Vector is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect
information from them.</p>

<h2>Your control over your data</h2>
<p>You can change your birth details at any time in Settings, and reset the app
completely, which erases the stored profile and all cached readings. Because we
hold no copy of your data, deleting the app is sufficient to delete everything.</p>

<h2>Changes</h2>
<p>If this policy changes, the updated version will be posted at this address with
a new date above.</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
